表格群组管理的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('GroupInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table GroupInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: GroupInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table GroupInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
GroupID nchar(10) not null,
GroupName nchar(10) null,
Header varchar(50) null,
Action varchar(50) null,
MemberNum int null,
Remark varchar(50) null,
aDate datetime not null constraint DF_GroupInfo_aDate default getdate(),
mDate datetime not null constraint DF_GroupInfo_mDate default getdate(),
constraint PK_GroupInfo primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go
